name: Pro Wrestling X \u2013 Bringing back classic wrestling gaming!
blurb: Pro wrestling video games lost their classic style of fun over a decade ago. We're bringing it back with Pro Wrestling X.

rewards.reward: Show us some love, buy us a beverage. Caffeine and Slurpees ain't cheap. We'll credit you in-game as a drinking buddy, and we'll be sure to toast in your honor.

More fun than a coconut to the skull! Digital download of Pro Wrestling X + current version of our first release, Uprising. We'll throw in some desktop wallpapers just for fun. Credit in-game as a Kickstarter backer.

EARLY BIRD SPECIAL, THIS TIER WILL HIT $25 WHEN FULL! OK, we'll send you a Newsletter Anthology PDF too  - over 550 newsletters - and "The Making of the Pro Wrestling X Kickstarter" podcast.

OK, rich guy. You could have paid a kid to dribble a basketball 10 times (and kicked the ball at bounce #9) for your own amusement. Instead, you gave the money to us. As a reward, character designer Mel will send you an *awesome* calacas figure (see example pics in the description). We'll also put in you IN THE GAME as a member of the crowd. (PLEASE SEE SHIPPING DETAILS ON THIS PAGE)

You're clearly a million dollar playboy with a different luxury car for every day of the week. We're thrilled to know you! Get all the digital downloads, the Create-a-Wrestler, a CUSTOM CALACAS figure, free games FOR LIFE, and everything detailed at kickstarter.prowrestlingx.com.

We're not worthy, Billionaire Ted. As a token of our esteem, please accept a CHAMPIONSHIP BELT designed by our good friend Jesse Justice (who has designed belts for Shane Helms and Jeff Hardy), along with all the rewards listed at kickstarter.prowrestlingx.com. It's the least we can do to reward your generosity.
